queries.query: INSERT INTO `api_accesslogs` (`vIPAddress`, `vAPIName`, `vAPIURL`, `dAccessDate`, `vPlatform`, `vBrowser`, `vFileName`) VALUES ('103.142.120.95', 'user_list', 'http://18.211.58.235/canoodle/WS/user_list', '2020-11-18 07:49:48', 'Unknown OS Platform', 'Unknown Browser', 'user_list-1605685788.json')
UPDATE `users` SET `dtUpdatedAt` = NOW(), `vDescription` = 'This is me' WHERE `iUserId` = '5'

SELECT `p`.`iMediaId` AS `media_id`,`p`.`vMediaType` AS `media_type`,`p`.`vMediaUrl` AS `media_url`,`p`.`vMediaName` AS `media_name`,`p`.`vMediaFile` AS `media_file`,`p`.`dtAddedAt` AS `p_updated_date`,(DATE_FORMAT(p.dtAddedAt,"%b %d %Y")) AS added_at FROM `user_media` AS `p` WHERE `p`.`iUserId` = '5'

SELECT `p`.`iMediaId` AS `media_id`,`p`.`iUserId` AS `user_id`,`p`.`vMediaType` AS `media_type`,`p`.`vMediaUrl` AS `media_url`,`p`.`vMediaName` AS `media_name`,`p`.`vMediaFile` AS `media_file`,`p`.`vVideoThumbnail` AS `video_thumbnail`,`p`.`dtAddedAt` AS `p_updated_date`,(DATE_FORMAT(p.dtAddedAt,"%b %d %Y")) AS added_at FROM `user_media` AS `p` WHERE `p`.`iUserId` = '5' AND `p`.`vMediaType` = 'video/mp4' AND `p`.`vMediaUrl` = '' AND `p`.`vVideoThumbnail` = ''
